ministrative area of your Joomla website.</li>\n<li><strong>Step3: </strong> Go to Extensions Manager from top menu: Extensions( or, Extensions Manager ) -&gt; Manage.</li>\n<li><strong>Step4: </strong> Now find Browse(Choose File) button under Upload &amp; Install Joomla Extension and hit the Browse button, browse to the location of downloaded Joomla Joomla Services Showcase Module (zip file) on your local computer, and press the Upload &amp; Install button.</li>\n<li><strong>Step5: </strong> When you install the extension successfully, go to: Extensions ( or, Extensions Manager ) &gt;&gt; Modules (or, Module Manager).</li>\n<li><strong>Step6: </strong> Now Config Your Module</li>\n<li><strong>Step5.</strong> After Complete configure the extensions hit Save &amp; Close button.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class="clearfix" style="margin-top: 70px;"></div>\n<p><strong>To Basic configure the Joomla Services Showcase Module, please follow our guide line:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Step1: </strong> Go to Extensions Manager from top menu: Extensions ( or, Extensions Manager ) -&gt; Modules ( or, Module Manager ).</li>\n<li><strong>Step2: </strong> Find the Joomla Services Showcase Module and enter.</li>\n<li><strong>Step3: </strong> Set Module Position from drop down list.</li>\n<li><strong>Step4: </strong> Set Module Status Published.</li>\n<li><strong>Step5: </strong> Select menu from Menu Assignment Tab.</li>\n<li><strong>Step6: </strong> Now create article category for service.</li>\n<li><strong>Step6: </strong> Create new Article with intro image  and Add assign service category.</li>\n<li><strong>Step6: </strong> Now Select a category in module source tab.</li>\n<li><strong>Step7: </strong> Now explore all settings tab and set parameter as your own demand. Please read option tooltip information carefully for configure.</li>\n<li><strong>Step8: </strong>Now Save and enjoy.</li>\n</ul>\n<div class="clearfix" style="margin:35px 0"></div>\n<div class="row">\n<div class="col-